headline: Jabil Recognizes Nordson Electronics Solutions with the 2024 Best Strategic Supplier Award
summary: CARLSBAD, Calif., February 05, 2025--Jabil awards Nordson Electronics Solutions for Best Strategic Supplier, related to fluid dispensing systems used in electronics manufacturing
